]] || Verses of Desire || ancient [[book]] about [[human sexual behavior]] by [[V\u0101tsy\u0101yana]]\n|-\n|''[[Katamari Damacy]]''|| \u584a\u9b42 || [[Japanese language|Japanese]] || ''Clump Soul'' || video game by [[Namco]]\n|-\n|[[Kebra Nagast]]|| \u12ad\u1265\u1228 \u1290\u1308\u1225\u1275 || [[Ge'ez]] || Glory of Kings || [[Ethiopia]]n's [[national epic]]\n|-\n|[[Keine Lust]]||  || [[German language|German]] || No Desire (German idiom for \"I don't feel like it.\") || song by [[Rammstein]]\n|-\n|[[Kindertotenlieder]]||  || [[German language|German]] || Songs of Dead Children || [[song cycle]] by [[Gustav Mahler]]\n|-\n|''[[Kraftwerk (album)|Kraftwerk]]''||  || [[German language|German]] || ''Power Station ''|| debut album by [[Kraftwerk]]\n|-\n|[[Moscow Kremlin|Kremlin]]|| \u041a\u0440\u0435\u043c\u043b\u044c || [[Russian language|Russian]] || Fortress || historic fortified complex at the heart of [[Moscow]], [[Russia]]\n|-\n|''[[Kundun]]''|| \u0f66\u0f90\u0f74\u0f0b\u0f58\u0f51\u0f74\u0f53\u0f0b || [[Standard Tibetan|Tibetan]] || ''The Presence'' || film directed by [[Martin Scorsese]]\n|-\n|''[[La Boh\u00e8me]]''||  || [[French language|French]] || ''The Bohemian'' || opera by [[Giacomo Puccini]]\n|-\n|''[[La cr\u00e9ation du monde]]''||  || [[French language|French]] || ''The Creation of the World'' || [[ballet]] by [[Darius Milhaud]]\n|-\n|[[La cucaracha]]||  || [[Spanish language|Spanish]] || The [[Cockroach]] || [[traditional]] song\n|-\n|''[[La dame aux cam\u00e9lias]]''||  || [[French language|French]] || ''The Lady of the Camellias'' || novel by [[Alexandre Dumas, fils]]\n|-\n|[[La Damoiselle \u00e9lue]]||  || [[French language|French]] || [[The Blessed Damozel]] ||cantata by [[Claude Debussy]] after poem by [[Dante Gabriel Rossetti]]\n|-\n|''[[La Dolce Vita]]''||  || [[Italian language|Italian]] || ''The Sweet Life'' || film directed by [[Federico Fellini]]\n|-\n|''[[La finta giardiniera]]''||  || [[Italian language|Italian]] || ''The Pretend Garden-