er|title=Encyclopedia of Diasporas|chapter=Armenian Diaspora|date=2005|publisher=[[Springer Science+Business Media|Springer]]|isbn=978-0-306-48321-9|page=40}}</ref>\n\n}}\n\n==Bibliography==\n===Books on San Lazzaro===\n*Peratoner, Alberto (2007; 2015). ''From Ararat to San Lazzaro. A Cradle of Armenian Spirituality and Culture in the Venice Lagoon. -'' Contributions by Fr. Vertanes Oulouhodjan and H.E. Boghos Levon Zekiyan. Venice: Congregazione Armena Mechitarista - Casa Editrice Armena.\n*{{cite book|last=Issaverdenz|first=James|title=The Island of San Lazzaro, Or, The Armenian Monastery Near Venice|date=1890|publisher=Armenian typography of San Lazzaro|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=6OAVAAAAYAAJ&printsec=frontcover|ref=harv}}\n*{{cite book|last=Langlois|first=Victor|title=The Armenian Monastery of St. Lazarus-Venice|year=1874|publisher=Typography of St. Lazarus|location=Venice|url=https://archive.org/details/descriptionarme00langgoog|authorlink=Victor Langlois|ref=harv}}\n\n===Articles on San Lazzaro===\n*{{cite news|last=Levonian Cole|first=Teresa|title=San Lazzaro degli Armeni: A slice of Armenia in Venice|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/travel/europe/san-lazzaro-degli-armeni-a-slice-of-armenia-in-venice-10429928.html|work=[[The Independent]]|date=31 July 2015|url-status=dead|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171103085107/https://www.independent.co.uk/travel/europe/san-lazzaro-degli-armeni-a-slice-of-armenia-in-venice-10429928.html|archivedate=3 November 2017|ref={{harvid|Levonian Cole|2015a}}}} \n*{{cite news|last=Levonian Cole|first=Teresa|title=The monk keeping his Armenian heritage alive in Venice|url=https://www.ft.com/content/7477cf7e-56e2-11e5-9846-de406ccb37f2|work=[[Financial Times]]|date=25 September 2015|archiveurl=https://archive.org/details/VeniceArmenianMonk|archivedate=29 December 2017|ref={{harvid|Levonian Cole|2015b}}}}\n*{{cite journal|last1=Gordan|first1=Lucy|title=The Venetian Island of St. Lazarus: Where Armenian Culture Su